    dc:description "Figs. 6-10. Protonemura neofiligera. 6. Male terminalia, dorsal. 7. Male hypoproct and vesicle, ventral. 8. Male left paraproct, ventrocaudal. 9. Male terminalia, lateral. 10. Female sterna 7-9, ventral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4753175/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4753173>
    dc:description "Figs. 1-5. Protonemura fansipanensis. 1. Male terminalia, dorsal. 2. Male terminalia, ventral. 3. Male terminalia, lateral. 4. Male paraprocts. 5. Female terminalia, ventral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4753173/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

